children.name: Rules
children.text:
Forever caked in a healthy layer of dirt, this heater shield's distinct scoop shape speaks volumes of its history as a giant's trowel.
While holding this +1 shield you can cast the Mold Earth Spell.
As an action you can activate the shield's ancient wards, giving all plant creatures disadvantage to attack you for one minute. After this is activated it cannot be used this way again until the next dawn.
